{"tid":1027637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【渣馬2019】Samsung印紀念襟章　跑手斥浪費　回收122套速遞寄回","createTime":"2019-02-19T02:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T07:34:30.000Z","uid":45148,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e10f89bba6dd696f680fe10fc15942c388a16366","tid":1027637,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"渣打馬拉松每年都會向跑手派發選手包，今年贊助商Samsung印製的打氣襟章，印有「PLAY」、「HAHA」、「LOL」等字句，不少跑手批評紀念品「唔等駛」，跑友廖先生發起號召回收行動，最終收集122套襟章，並即日將紀念品以速遞方式寄回Samsung。他回應《香港01》查詢時表示，希望大會及贊助商可收到訊息，不會再派發與跑步無關的紀念品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCeQe5o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCeQe5o.jpg&h=5871fd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfTESR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtfTESR8.jpg&h=c8a645a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ccY8qA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ccY8qA.jpg&h=14c4e957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/296051/渣馬2019-samsung印紀念襟章-跑手斥浪費-回收122套速遞寄回\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F296051%2F%E6%B8%A3%E9%A6%AC2019-samsung%E5%8D%B0%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E8%A5%9F%E7%AB%A0-%E8%B7%91%E6%89%8B%E6%96%A5%E6%B5%AA%E8%B2%BB-%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6122%E5%A5%97%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E%E5%AF%84%E5%9B%9E&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEpWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=b1fa6cac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/296051/渣馬2019-samsung印紀念襟章-跑手斥浪費-回收122套速遞寄回</a>"},{"pid":"43d1d3f452dbaa67094a11f8c9ac8008fdecd2cb","tid":1027637,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f07e9181e6b31d9b0ab09b8a9b7b2fd36b44803","tid":1027637,"uid":119579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"我即日扔咗<img s